			<div class="c-grav"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a91f333aa8ca4f4fa6e363d7d1404a07?s=60&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-60' height='60' width='60' /></div>
