			<li class="comment byuser comment-author-curtisvalentine odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 highlander-comment" id="comment-233" >
			<div class="c-grav"><img alt='' src='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/2a76c76b9b5fd8a899d7358141b24ca6?s=60&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-60' height='60' width='60' /></div>
